text: te brasenbae kar ngeak chenh robsa puokke bangk kar lombak dl anak( mou ham meat) haey brasenbae anak meanolotthopheap svengork phlauv chaul tow knong dei ryy chondaer laeng towleu mekh ning meanolotthopheap noam phosdo tang namuoy mk bangheanh puokke( chaur anak thveu choh) . brasenbae a l laoh mean chetnea trong pitchea bramoulophdom puokke teangoasa aoy sthet leu kar changaoulobangheanh . hetonih anak min trauv sthet knongchamnaom puok lngongkhlaw laey
